Padre-Plugin-Git

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

WARNING

This plugin relies on the command 'git' to be present. There's no check in the
installation script that git is installed. You have to ensure that yourself.

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Padre::Plugin::Git

